edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.app

Class ErrorMessageRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.app.ErrorMessageRegistry

  • public final class ErrorMessageRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the central registry for all error messages that should have a static message. This is needed especially for REST tests to verify that not only an exception of the expected type is thrown, but also for the expected reason.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Matthias Dressel, Michael Hitzker, Markus Hoefler, Andreas Loeffler, Timo Schmidt
